  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Quora?",
  "response": "Quora is a question-and-answer website where users can ask questions, provide answers, and engage in discussions on a wide range of topics. The name \"Quora\" is derived from the Latin word \"quorum,\" which means \"of whom\" or \"of which.\" The platform aims to connect people with knowledge and those seeking it, fostering a community-driven approach to sharing information and insights. Users can upvote or downvote answers, follow topics, and follow other users to curate their feed based on their interests. Quora covers a diverse array of subjects, including technology, health, education, hobbies, and more.",
